d/invalid/dirty/etc). On groups, this includes the additional\nclass ng-submitted.</p>\n<p>该指令自动应用于 Angular 表单组，基于控件的状态（有效、无效、脏等）设置 CSS 类。</p>\n\n  </section>\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatusGroup#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatus\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgControlStatus</a></code></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatusGroup#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/NgControlStatusGroup#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/FormGroupName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formGroupName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/FormArrayName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formArrayName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/NgModelGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModelGroup</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[formGroup]</code></li>\n    <li><code>form<i>:not([ngNoForm])</i></code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/NgForm\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngForm</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n-->\n<!-